t the wrath of Trump, and fear of retribution, have made these familiar rit=
uals even more obsequious than I could ever have imagined.=C2=A0</p><p styl=
e=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bot=
